1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,000
An AI agent is controlling this PC —
from another machine.

2
00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:07,000
One command turns a Windows box
into an MCP server:  npx winreach-mcp

3
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:11,000
It opens a secure Cloudflare tunnel —
no inbound firewall holes.

4
00:00:11,000 --> 00:00:15,000
Any MCP agent connects over HTTP
with its own bearer key.

5
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:20,000
Run real PowerShell, remotely —
as a single MCP tool call.

6
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:25,000
Move files both ways —
sandboxed and hash-verified.

7
00:00:25,000 --> 00:00:30,000
Capture the screen
whenever the agent needs to look.

8
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:35,000
And drive the mouse and keyboard
like a human — full computer use.

9
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:40,000
Every agent gets its own key and role:
admin · operator · readonly.

10
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:45,000
A regex command policy blocks
dangerous commands — live.

11
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:50,000
And every action is written
to an append-only audit log.

12
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:55,000
WinReach — give your AI agent
its own Windows machine.
